1. Edit the buildoptions file and change the lines for CC,CXX,F90 to specify the names of the compilers to use.
      
2. Edit the three lines MPI_TOP, MPI_INCDIR, and MPI_LIBS to specify the location of the MPI library.  Optionally, you can use
   the mpicc,mpicxx,mpif90 commands in step 1 and leave these lines blank.
   
3. "Make" should compile the code and place an executable called flowsolver in the bin folder